title: Sonata Arctica - Tricky Beans Collection (+Demos)
description:
A collection of Sonata Arctica's early music and demos from 1995-1998.


The first 8 songs are from the earliest Tricky Beans demos, and the second 8 songs are from the "Tricky Means" demos that later became famous Sonata Arctica songs.


I've put them in no particular order, other than the two halves.


1. Blackout
2. Addict
3. Apartment 54
4. A Bit Lost
5. Find A Gun
6. I'm Haunted
7. Friend Till The End
8. Frog Feet
9. Fullmoon (demo)
10. Letter To Dana (demo)
11. Peacemaker (demo)
12. Shy (demo)
13. Tallulah (demo)
14. UnOpened (demo)
15. 8th Commandment (demo)
16. Mary-Lou (demo)


These are a must-have for any die-hard Sonata Arctica fan!


File type: MP3 (320kbs)
File size: 135MB



Tony Kakko - Vocals/Keyboards
Jani Liimatainen - Guitar
Marko Paasikoski - Guitar
Tommy Portimo - Drums
Pentti Peura/Janne Kivilahti - Bass
